sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client App
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant GQL as GraphQL Server
    participant WS as WebSocket Handler
    participant DB as Database
    participant PubSub as PubSub Engine

    Note over Client,PubSub: GraphQL Subscription Lifecycle

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,GW: Phase 1 - Connection Initialization
        Client->>GW: HTTP Upgrade Request (ws://)
        GW->>GW: Validate Origin & Rate Limit
        GW->>WS: Forward WebSocket Handshake
        WS-->>GW: 101 Switching Protocols
        GW-->>Client: WebSocket Connection Established
        Client->>WS: connection_init {authToken: "jwt-xyz"}
        WS->>GQL: Validate Authentication Token
        GQL-->>WS: Token Valid (user: alice)
        WS-->>Client: connection_ack {keepAlive: 30000}
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,PubSub: Phase 2 - Subscription Registration
        Client->>WS: subscribe {id: "sub-1", query: "subscription { orderUpdated(userId: 42) { id status estimatedDelivery } }"}
        WS->>GQL: Parse & Validate Subscription Query
        GQL->>GQL: Check Field Permissions for User
        GQL->>PubSub: Register Listener on "orders:42" channel
        PubSub-->>GQL: Subscription Registered
        GQL-->>WS: Subscription Active (sub-1)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 220)
        Note over Client,PubSub: Phase 3 - Real-time Data Push
        Note over DB: External event: Order status changes
        DB->>PubSub: Publish event: orders:42 {status: "PREPARING"}
        PubSub->>GQL: Notify Subscriber (sub-1)
        GQL->>DB: Resolve subscription fields (fetch latest data)
        DB-->>GQL: {id: 1001, status: "PREPARING", eta: "12:30"}
        GQL->>GQL: Apply field-level authorization
        GQL-->>WS: next {id: "sub-1", data: {orderUpdated: {...}}}
        WS-->>Client: Push: Order is being prepared

        Note over DB: Another event: Rider assigned
        DB->>PubSub: Publish event: orders:42 {status: "OUT_FOR_DELIVERY"}
        PubSub->>GQL: Notify Subscriber (sub-1)
        GQL->>DB: Resolve subscription fields
        DB-->>GQL: {id: 1001, status: "OUT_FOR_DELIVERY", eta: "12:15", rider: "Bob"}
        GQL-->>WS: next {id: "sub-1", data: {orderUpdated: {...}}}
        WS-->>Client: Push: Order out for delivery

        Note over DB: Final event: Order delivered
        DB->>PubSub: Publish event: orders:42 {status: "DELIVERED"}
        PubSub->>GQL: Notify Subscriber (sub-1)
        GQL->>DB: Resolve subscription fields
        DB-->>GQL: {id: 1001, status: "DELIVERED", deliveredAt: "12:10"}
        GQL-->>WS: next {id: "sub-1", data: {orderUpdated: {...}}}
        WS-->>Client: Push: Order delivered!
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over Client,PubSub: Phase 4 - Unsubscribe & Cleanup
        Client->>WS: complete {id: "sub-1"}
        WS->>GQL: Unsubscribe sub-1
        GQL->>PubSub: Remove Listener on "orders:42"
        PubSub-->>GQL: Listener Removed
        GQL-->>WS: Subscription Ended (sub-1)

        Note over Client,WS: Connection Keep-Alive
        loop Every 30 seconds
            WS-->>Client: ka (keep-alive ping)
            Client->>WS: pong
        end

        Client->>WS: connection_terminate
        WS->>GQL: Cleanup all subscriptions for session
        WS-->>Client: Connection Closed
    end
